# MeshPaw Environment Configuration

# === Core AI Features ===
# Required for Mesh Brain (Local Room Summarization)
# Get your key at: https://aistudio.google.com/
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY="your_google_gemini_api_key_here"

# === Auth0 Identity Integration ===
# Required for connecting decentralized nodes to verified Web2 identities.
VITE_AUTH0_DOMAIN="your_tenant.us.auth0.com"
VITE_AUTH0_CLIENT_ID="your_auth0_client_id_here"

# ⚠️ Note on Auth0 "Development Keys" Warning:
# When you log in, you might see a warning from Auth0: "One or more of your connections are currently using Auth0 development keys and should not be used in production."
# Why? By default, Auth0 uses test credentials for Google/GitHub social logins.
# How to fix: 
# 1. Go to Auth0 Dashboard -> Authentication -> Social.
# 2. Click on Google/GitHub and enter your own real Client ID and Client Secret (obtained from Google Cloud Console / GitHub Developer Settings).
# 3. The warning will disappear.
